history.proof: intro H. induction A as [| a A IHA]. - left. intros x H0. inversion H0. - destruct (H a) as [Ha | Ha]. + destruct (IHA) as [IHAH | IHAH]. * left. intros x [H1 | H1]. subst. apply Ha. apply IHAH. apply H1. * right. intros H2. apply IHAH. intros x H3. apply H2. right. apply H3. + right. intros H0. apply Ha. apply H0. left. reflexivity.

original: intro H. induction A as [| a A IHA]. - left. intros x H0. inversion H0. - destruct (H a) as [Ha | Ha]. + destruct (IHA) as [IHAH | IHAH]. * left. intros x [H1 | H1]. { subst. apply Ha. } { apply IHAH. apply H1. } * right. intros H2. apply IHAH. intros x H3. apply H2. right. apply H3. + right. intros H0. apply Ha. apply H0. left. reflexivity.
